{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;The Abyss&quot;</strong> plunges players into a dark and unsettling world where the line between reality and nightmare blurs. After a severe car accident, the protagonist falls into a deep coma and awakens in a shadowy, eerie realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this <strong>two-level demo</strong>, players take control of the protagonist, exploring the initial depths of this grim world in first-person perspective. Throughout these levels, they will face unspeakable horrors, solve twisted puzzles, and begin to uncover fragments of the protagonist's story, revealing dark secrets intertwined with the very nature of the Abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The two levels offer an intense introductory experience, with claustrophobic and surreal environments that challenge the player\u2019s perception and sanity. Each terrifying encounter and completed challenge brings the player closer to the essence of this dark world, hinting at the traumas and inner demons keeping the protagonist trapped.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to descend into <strong>the first two levels of the Abyss</strong> and confront the darkness lurking within?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732905090","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376100/page.bg.jpg?t=1732905090","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376100/8c035a67723d90ef633f9c78ca5ed232e8cf8210/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732905090","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376100/8c035a67723d90ef633f9c78ca5ed232e8cf8210/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732905090","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quo